de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.multilingual

Class SenseAxis

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tudarmstadt.ukp.lmf.model.multilingual.SenseAxis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IHasID

    public class SenseAxis
extends java.lang.Object
implements IHasID
    SenseAxis is a class representing the relationship between different closely related Sense instances in different languages and implements approach based on the interlingual pivot. The purpose is to describe the translation of lexemes, represented through LexicalEntry instances, from one language to another.
    Author:
    Zijad Maksuti
